These instructions allow you to upgrade from fofork 1.5.x to 1.6.y

If you wish to upgrade from the 1.0 or 1.1 branches, you can either
1. First upgrade to version 1.5 (using the upgrade script distributed with
	the 1.5 branch releases), and the upgrade to version 1.6 OR
2. Uninstall your existing installation, and run a clean install

PLEASE backup your existing database and/or logs before proceeding.

1. Upload the file 'upgrade.php' from the 1.6.y branch to the root of your web server
2. Browse to /upgrade.php.  Enter your admin password, and click upgrade
3. Delete all the 1.5 branch code on your webserver, and replace with 
	the 1.6 branch code
